Plot:

"It's school time again, and the team is prepping for the big game. But for some reason, they just can't shake their losing streak. That's where the girls of Team Spirit come in. They've just got to give all those guys the lift they need to get out there and win one for the school. The girls give their all and they give it to anyone who happens to walk by. Like the coach, the quarterback, the water boy, even each other. Team Spirit features a whole gym full of really, really young girls who just love to take it off and show you what they've got. And they've got a lot, and it's really, really young and new and fresh and pure. So let's hear it for the team!"
